title: The Gavin McInnes Show 2016-01-20 Episode 80 Damien Echols
description:
*** CAUTION: 100% UNCENSORED CONTENT!!! ***

-NOT FOR VIEWING BY CHILDREN OR THE FAINT OF HEART-

The always outspoken and "controversial" Gavin McInnes joins the Anthony Cumia Network - with new shows twice a week. In addition to co-founding VICE, the author, actor, podcast host, and political pundit is at the forefront of the modern "anti-PC" movement and a perfect match for the cutting edge and newly emerging ACN.

Guests: Damien Echols, Terry Schappert, Trailer Park Boys, Terry from FUBAR, Mercedes Carrera

Episode 80: Today on TGMS; West Memphis Three survivor Damien Echols is in-studio for the full episode, National Guard Master Sergeant Terry Schappert is interviewed, Gavin video chats with The Trailer Park Boys, Terry from the movie FUBAR, and then closes out the packed episode featuring Happy Endings with Mercedes Carrera.
